name: iPowerUp
overview: iPowerUp is an award-winning designer and engineer of electronic accessories for smart mobile devices. Since getting incorporated in 2007 they have acquired world-class executives and design teams and have established a core methodology allowing for rapid development to bring new products to market. With its patented technology iPowerUp has made its focus to provide the highest quality products in each mobile category using a combination of their own proprietary designs and unique original design manufacturer partnerships. iPowerUp has become admired by customers and mobile industry experts for its innovative and stylish mobile charging solutions. Today, iPower products are created to work with the industry’s leading mobile devices bringing diversity, value and satisfaction to its customers, business partners and shareholders. These products are available through D&H distribution, Radio Shack, Hudson News and other major retailers worldwide.
